33 BT::NodeStatus SetLocations::tick()
34 {
35  // Read YAML file
36  std::string yaml_file;
37  ros::param::get("location_file", yaml_file);
38  ROS_INFO("%s", yaml_file.c_str());
39  YAML::Node locations = YAML::LoadFile(yaml_file)["path_locations"];
40  for (YAML::const_iterator it = locations.begin(); it != locations.end(); ++it)
41  {
42  std::array<float, 3> entry = it->second.as<std::array<float, 3>>();
43  PathLocation location = {entry[0], entry[1], entry[2]};
44  path_queue_->Enqueue(QueueSide::back, location);
45  }
46 
47  int num_locs = path_queue_->GetQueue().size();
48  if (num_locs == 0)
49  {
50  ROS_ERROR("[%s] No path locations found!", this->name().c_str());
51  return BT::NodeStatus::FAILURE;
52  }
53  setOutput("num_locs", num_locs);
54  ROS_INFO("[%s] Found %d locations.", this->name().c_str(), num_locs);
55 
56  YAML::Node fixed_locations = YAML::LoadFile(yaml_file)["fixed_locations"];
57  std::array<float, 3> entry_basket_change_location = (fixed_locations["empty_basket_location"]).as<std::array<float, 3>>();
58  PathLocation basket_change_location = {entry_basket_change_location[0], entry_basket_change_location[1], entry_basket_change_location[2]};
59  path_queue_->SetEmptyBasketLocation(basket_change_location);
60 
61  std::array<float, 3> entry_recharge_location = (fixed_locations["recharge_location"]).as<std::array<float, 3>>();
62  PathLocation recharge_location = {entry_recharge_location[0], entry_recharge_location[1], entry_recharge_location[2]};
63  path_queue_->SetRechargeLocation(recharge_location);
64 
65  return BT::NodeStatus::SUCCESS;
66 }

112 BT::NodeStatus GetLocationFromQueue::tick()
113 {
114  if (path_queue_->GetQueue().empty())
115  {
116  ROS_ERROR("[%s] No more locations!", this->name().c_str());
117  return BT::NodeStatus::FAILURE;
118  }
119  else
120  {
121  PathLocation target_location = path_queue_->GetQueue().front();
122  setOutput("target_location", target_location);
123  path_queue_->Dequeue(QueueSide::front);
124  return BT::NodeStatus::SUCCESS;
125  }
126 }

177 BT::NodeStatus GoToPose::onStart()
178 {
179  LOG_NAV_START(this->name());
180  manipulator_.MoveToDrivingPosition();
181  BT::Optional<PathLocation> loc = getInput<PathLocation>("loc");
182  ROS_INFO("[%s] next goal: x=%.2f y=%.2f w=%.2f", this->name().c_str(), loc->x, loc->y, loc->orientation);
183  goal_.target_pose.header.frame_id = "summit_xl_map";
184  goal_.target_pose.pose.position.x = loc->x;
185  goal_.target_pose.pose.position.y = loc->y;
186  goal_.target_pose.pose.orientation = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(0, 0, loc->orientation);
187  client_.sendGoal(goal_);
188  return BT::NodeStatus::RUNNING;
189 }

196 BT::NodeStatus GoToPose::onRunning()
197 {
198  actionlib::SimpleClientGoalState state = client_.getState();
199  if (state == actionlib::SimpleClientGoalState::SUCCEEDED)
200  {
201  ROS_DEBUG("[%s] reached goal", this->name().c_str());
202  LOG_NAV_STOP(this->name());
203  return BT::NodeStatus::SUCCESS;
204  }
205  else if (state == actionlib::SimpleClientGoalState::ACTIVE || state == actionlib::SimpleClientGoalState::PENDING)
206  {
207  return BT::NodeStatus::RUNNING;
208  }
209  else
210  {
211  LOG_NAV_STOP(this->name());
212  ROS_ERROR("[%s] Failed to reach goal!", this->name().c_str());
213  return BT::NodeStatus::FAILURE;
214  }
215 }

278 BT::NodeStatus SaveCurrentLocation::tick()
279 {
280  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped current_location = ba_helper::GetCurrentPoseInMapFrame(BASE_FRAME);
281  float rotation = ba_helper::ConvertQuaternionToAngle(current_location.pose.orientation);
282  if (tomato_queue_->GetReachableTomatoes().size() > 0)
283  {
284  PathLocation current_location_as_struct = {(float)current_location.pose.position.x, (float)current_location.pose.position.y, rotation};
285  path_queue_->Enqueue(QueueSide::front, current_location_as_struct);
286  }
287  else
288  {
289  path_queue_->Enqueue(QueueSide::front, path_queue_->Dequeue(QueueSide::front, false));
290  }
291  return BT::NodeStatus::SUCCESS;
292 }
